Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我到底还能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了改变那如狭隘庭园般的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗 相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无意识中被刻上的经验纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当站在悬崖边的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦难抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往更加宽广的领域\N往更深更大的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着无法预测的世界前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.25,0:01:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壮观！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.05,0:01:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是神体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过看起来神也会受伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心，水柱会治愈5-O的创伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}5-O：5A级O.P.A.T.S的略称
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个就是它们的残骸？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的机密资料
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是得到采访许可的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.45,0:02:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，不允许拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你一直在画什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么，与你无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要的话，我可以做你的模特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的好意，不必了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.66,0:02:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？你们那里流行的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小时候就有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}蒙古斑：黄种人出生时身上的色斑，多在1、2年后消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙古斑？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的还在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善哉，善哉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥，你在忙什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没处理完的事物要完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是放假吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在这里放松享乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不是享乐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里等我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨！精神好最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！如月博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天晚上在我家要开一个小聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做学者真是悠闲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.17,0:03:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚会？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是圣诞夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便庆祝你的升职
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有理由接受你庆贺吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么古板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔和大家聚在一起\N开心一下不是很好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多作战部的人都会去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如八云
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云他也回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位都会来吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，中你的计了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，各位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明晚7点恭候各位的光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞老人好像心情不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是驯鹿似乎不太高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然早了点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很贵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你工作一直很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，博士！快看！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒，好棒啊！真是太美了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是雪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有见过雪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我从来没有离开过这个岛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是有气象记录以来的第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会积雪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是明天圣诞夜也下雪就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热朗姆酒！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节原本是庆祝冬至的节日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是基督徒们却擅自把这一天变成了基督的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是无神论者吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗教和宗教活动可完全是两回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候，当渔夫的爷爷\N和我说他看到了一头白鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后他对我说“给你这个”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无缘无故地把他心爱的匕首给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下次出海捕鱼时，\N爷爷就再也没能回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该已经知道他就要死了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你，怎么想呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真有毅力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这样努力呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为我是为了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了工作而锻炼体力吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿的是什么衣服啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没办法啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我没带冬装！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个，收下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢，谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，这是哪儿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…那儿不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹！布奇！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做这种事是要负责任的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠！快点起床吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛！像老妈似的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据U-06的报告，\ND-1应该已经死亡了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结论还无法断定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是圣诞节，不会出问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值班守备没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在如月家好像要举行晚会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与我无关，说到这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不去见见他？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了，真是白色圣诞节呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定可以看到白色的圣诞树
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我第一次在雪地上留下脚印…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没伤着吧，惠？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然，这个鞋跟太高了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次会受伤的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…在我这个年纪…\N差不多就有这么高了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹明天就要到这儿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好相处啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会送礼物给你姐姐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:08:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是那么讨厌她，我姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很完美…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她也有像一般女孩那样比较笨的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前，好像有一个她非常喜欢的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像无法忘记他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能送给他的礼物还珍藏在她的抽屉里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事她一直无法忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很蠢是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像她还是一个小女孩似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得绫人君…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个，请收下！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:09:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以看看里面是什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！正是我想要的那个！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，那个…\N今天晚上在如月博士家的聚会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！我打算去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠也去是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么今天晚上见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…果然八云喜欢姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？我想不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能像姐姐的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，惠和遥非常像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们给人的感觉，还有表情…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上周击毁的D-1的碎片…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在还没有失去分子结合力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这表明某个保持着功能的部分\N很可能仍潜伏在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个有趣的案例啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究应该在这个事件处理完后再开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在消灭D-1才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了，紫东大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像你在新的部门工作也没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在工作的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你在意的人，你会不会紧张呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样？最近？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从前就是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我认识的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！好美的结晶石！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁送的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可能已经让他感到不舒服了\N因为那个印记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子…不冷吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道，因为我不是他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个，树博士！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天…久远怎么没有来？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她讨厌寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颤抖的思念…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的唇…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒冷的心是神媒柱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫东大尉，紫东大尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:13:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请立即到司令部\N今晚聚会见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直做得很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样，为什么还要欺负我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的错…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七森君…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你不给我温暖…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那块结晶石…果然是这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲、哥哥…不原谅我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太平洋发电机功能停止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为避免数据丢失进行数据中继
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切换至紧急备用电源
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在切换至紧急备用电源
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然发生了紧急事件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是它们！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,19，在Y-MARK点确认到量子反应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高度大约500米，不，还在增长中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与之前D-1相同的反应模式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信它就是这次寒流的成因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守备失职，是这样吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击！神名绫人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击？敌人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打败它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的工作吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，他怎么那样说话！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来以后再抱怨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.71,0:15:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:15:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会很快打倒它的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊，笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快反击啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样她会死的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会死？说什么傻话！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，在那个Dolem里面的…\N是小夜子小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样击毁它的话，\N小夜子小姐也会被杀的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事我可做不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击毁D-1最优先
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.51,0:16:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人命无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己在说什么吗？！你…！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TERRA可不是一个救生组织
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:17:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想救出七森君的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去创造一个奇迹吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon被直接击中！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon活动停止！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示器无法显示！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人君！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不被人爱的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好感受我心中的寒意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会出事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他是被选中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很温暖，遥的手套
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冻结的音色…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴弦跳动…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化为眩目的光芒！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从RahXephon那里传来高能量反应！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人君！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会创造的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会创造的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做奇迹的那种东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:18:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Xephon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin的光芒…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是灵魂的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认D-1已经消失！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认七森小夜子的生存反应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务结束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常温暖…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:19:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直像太阳一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种光…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，对不起…对不起！对不起…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的，在那次会议之后\N发生的事我都记不得了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灾难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士给我的挂坠…找不到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得收到那么贵重的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.41,0:20:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿些饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平常一样，蓝色的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有去做定期检查吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.21,0:20:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，olin很温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:20:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:20:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可有点嫉妒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…是惠送给你的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合适吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，总一…我们的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，惠…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐！小惠！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这双手套，非常暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那双手套…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.32,0:23:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那入口通往许多扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.82,0:23:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那扇门通向许多记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon 第九乐章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时之饲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.62,0:23:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界饱含着声音


